I Financial Highlights

Real Estate Transaction Services

Gross business profit in the Real Estate Business reached ¥50.0 billion on a consolidated basis for the first time since management integration in 2011. This was primarily due to growth in brokerage fees at SuMi TRUST Bank and Sumitomo Mitsui Trust Realty.

Real Estate Management and Administration Services

Sumitomo Mitsui Trust Reai Estate Investment Management undertakes management of private real estate funds. Sales of assets have been active in response to the recent rise in real estate prices, and the balance of assets under management has decreased slightly as a result.

Real Estate Infrastructure Services

Real estate securitization trusts and asset custody and gen- eral administration entrustments for investment companies are growing along with expansion of the REIT market, and We have secured the top place in Japan in terms of scale as a result.
